            <title>[LU-2826] Failure on test suite sanity test_18: read cache page error</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2826</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for sarah &amp;lt;sarah@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/cf24b96c-7785-11e2-987d-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/cf24b96c-7785-11e2-987d-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_18 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;== sanity test 18: touch .../f ; ls ... ================================ 14:29:49 (1360880989)&lt;br/&gt;
ls: reading directory /mnt/lustre: No data available&lt;br/&gt;
 sanity test_18: @@@@@@ FAIL:  &lt;br/&gt;
  Trace dump:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;14:29:51:Lustre: DEBUG MARKER: == sanity test 18: touch .../f ; ls ... ================================ 14:29:49 (1360880989)
14:29:51:LustreError: 651:0:(dir.c:421:ll_get_dir_page()) read cache page: [0x200000007:0x1:0x0] at 0: rc -61
14:29:51:LustreError: 651:0:(dir.c:583:ll_dir_read()) error reading dir [0x200000007:0x1:0x0] at 0: rc -61
14:29:51:Lustre: DEBUG MARKER: /usr/sbin/lctl mark  sanity test_18: @@@@@@ FAIL:  
14:29:51:Lustre: DEBUG MARKER: sanity test_18: @@@@@@ FAIL:
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
